WEBVTT

00:08:28.371 --> 00:08:30.002
And finally,

00:08:30.026 --> 00:08:32.208
I have to talk about bioengineering,

00:08:32.714 --> 00:08:38.767
an area of science that promises
to end disease before it even begins,

00:08:39.658 --> 00:08:44.078
to help us live longer,
fuller, healthier lives.

00:08:45.218 --> 00:08:48.340
And when you couple that
with implantable hardware,

00:08:48.364 --> 00:08:52.791
you are looking at the next incarnation
of human evolution.

00:08:52.815 --> 00:08:55.131
And all of that sounds great,

00:08:55.155 --> 00:08:57.456
until you figure out
where it's really going.

00:08:57.480 --> 00:08:58.659
One place:

00:08:59.133 --> 00:09:00.452
designer babies,